(175, '1.56 HMC DRIVE GLASS', '', '690', 100, 'product-featured-175.jpg', '<p>1. DRIVING AT NIGHT IS NOT THE SAME</p><p>Lights create more reflections and glare on our glasses at night. On the road, they can come from all directions and common sources like headlights, traffic lights, and street lamps.</p><p><br></p><p>Especially when you\'re driving at night, the additional reflections and glare can impact your vision and create discomfort.</p><p><br></p><p>2. THE EVERYDAY LENS FOR EVERY DRIVER</p><p>Whether you\'re a professional, casual or family driver, once night falls, you face the same distracting halos. Crizal drive lenses are specially designed to help you see clearly for a smoother ride day and night.</p><p><br></p><p>3.FULL CONFIDENCE ​EVEN AT NIGHT</p><p>Optimised for night driving, Crizal drive lenses have up to 90% less reflection(3) compared to ordinary lenses. This minimises the dangerous reflections from surrounding lights, so you can drive safely and confidently in low light.</p><p><br></p><p>4.SUPERIOR CLEAR VISION IN THE DAY</p><p>Benefit from wearing Crizal drive lenses in the day as well. They ensure confidence and comfort by maintaining clear and sharp vision all day long, in addition to enhancing your night vision.</p>', '<p>SPH +8.00 ~ -8.00 / CYP -PL ~ -5.00<br></p>', '', '', '', 2, 1, 1, 21, '255'),
